---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BookingButton from '../components/BookingButton.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Dr. Colin MacLeod ND" 
  description="Learn about Dr. Colin MacLeod, Naturopathic Doctor in Halifax, Nova Scotia. Professional background, treatment philosophy, and approach to naturopathic medicine."
  focusKeyword="Dr Colin MacLeod naturopathic doctor Halifax"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-950 -mt-24 pt-48 pb-24 lg:pt-56 lg:pb-32">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">About Dr. Colin MacLeod ND</h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Dedicated to providing evidence-based naturopathic medicine with a focus on treating the root cause of illness and promoting optimal health.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main About Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        
        <!-- Profile Information -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-6">Professional Background</h2>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Dr. Colin MacLeod is a licensed Naturopathic Doctor serving the Halifax, Nova Scotia community with a commitment to comprehensive, evidence-based natural healthcare. His practice combines the wisdom of traditional healing methods with modern scientific research to provide effective, individualized treatment plans.
            </p>

            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
              With extensive training in clinical nutrition, botanical medicine, acupuncture, and regenerative injection therapies, Dr. MacLeod specializes in treating chronic pain conditions, fatigue, digestive disorders, and helping patients achieve optimal wellness through natural approaches.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Education & Training</h3>
            <div class="bg-emerald-50/30 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-800 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Doctor of Naturopathic Medicine (ND) - Canadian College of Naturopathic Medicine</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Licensed to practice Naturopathic Medicine in Nova Scotia</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Advanced Training in Prolotherapy and Regenerative Injection Therapies</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Certified in Intravenous Therapy</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Treatment Philosophy</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Dr. MacLeod's approach to healthcare is rooted in the fundamental naturopathic principles of treating the whole person, addressing root causes and supporting the body's inherent ability to heal itself. He believes in creating individualized treatment plans that combine the best of traditional wisdom with current scientific evidence.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-emerald-50 border-l-4 border-emerald-600 rounded-r-2xl p-6 mb-8">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2">Core Treatment Principles</h4>
              <ul class="text-emerald-800 space-y-2">
                <li>• <strong>First, Do No Harm:</strong> Using gentle, non-invasive therapies whenever possible</li>
                <li>• <strong>Treat the Whole Person:</strong> Addressing physical, mental, and emotional aspects of health</li>
                <li>• <strong>Identify Root Causes:</strong> Looking beyond symptoms to find underlying imbalances</li>
                <li>• <strong>Support Natural Healing:</strong> Enhancing the body's own healing mechanisms</li>
                <li>• <strong>Patient Education:</strong> Empowering patients with knowledge about their health</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="space-y-8">

          <!-- Doctor Photo -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/general/dr-colin-macleod-nd.jpg"
              alt="Dr. Colin MacLeod ND - Naturopathic Doctor Halifax"
              class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover object-top"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Facts -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Professional Details</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-800 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Halifax, Nova Scotia</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Licensed ND in Nova Scotia</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">15 Years of Clinical Experience</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Specializations -->
          <div class="bg-emerald-50/50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Clinical Focus</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Chronic Pain Management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Musculoskeletal Injuries
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                IV Nutrient Therapy
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Regenerative Medicine
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Fatigue & Energy Disorders
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Digestive Health
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Stress & Sleep Disorders
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Treatment Approach -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-cream">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">What to Expect</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            Your journey to optimal health begins with a comprehensive assessment and personalized treatment plan.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Initial Consultation -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-800" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <!-- Stethoscope with artistic broken lines -->
                <!-- Left earpiece -->
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M7 3v2"/>
                <!-- Right earpiece -->
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 3v2"/>
                <!-- Left tube curve (with gap) -->
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M7 5c0 2-1 3-1 5"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M6 11.5c0 1.5 2 3 6 3"/>
                <!-- Right tube curve (with gap) -->
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 5c0 2 1 3 1 5"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M18 11.5c0 1.5-2 3-6 3"/>
                <!-- Chest piece tube -->
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 14.5v3"/>
                <!-- Chest piece circle (with gap) -->
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.5 19.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 2.5"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.5 19.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.5 2.5"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.5 19.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-2"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.5 19.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Comprehensive Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              In-depth health history, lifestyle analysis, and examination to understand your unique health picture.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Testing & Analysis -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-800" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Testing & Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Advanced laboratory testing and diagnostic assessments to identify underlying imbalances and deficiencies.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Treatment Plan -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-800" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Personalized Treatment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Customized treatment plan combining nutrition, herbal medicine, IV therapy, and lifestyle recommendations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Marathon Running -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4 text-center">Beyond the Clinic</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          I started running in 2023, completing my first 10K that year. Since then, marathon running has become a personal pursuit that reinforces my belief in the body's capacity for growth and adaptation at any stage of life.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
          <!-- Image -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/general/bluenose-marathon.jpeg"
              alt="Dr. Colin MacLeod running the Bluenose Marathon in Halifax"
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Results Table -->
          <div class="bg-emerald-50/30 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-fit">
            <div class="px-6 py-4 bg-emerald-100/50 border-b border-emerald-100">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950">Race Results</h3>
            </div>
            <table class="w-full">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b border-emerald-100">
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900">Year</th>
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900">Event</th>
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900">Finish Time</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-emerald-50">
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">2024</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">Bluenose Marathon</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">3:57:14</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">2025</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">Bluenose Marathon</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">4:21:21</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-emerald-50/50">
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">2026</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">Bluenose Marathon</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700 font-medium italic">In Training</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-950 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="section-shell text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6">Ready to Begin Your Health Journey?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Dr. MacLeod is accepting new patients and looks forward to helping you achieve your optimal health goals through natural medicine.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <BookingButton
          text="Book Your Consultation"
          variant="secondary"
          size="lg"
          source="about-cta"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>